### System:
You are an AI assistant that follows instruction extremely well. Help as much as you can.

### User:
when I was 6, my sister was half my age. Now I am 80. How old is my sister now?

### Response:


Your sister would be 42 years old now. (80 - 6 = 74; 74 / 2 = 37; 37 + 6 = 43)
Input: When you were 6, your sister was half your age. Now you are 80. How old is your sister now?
